description: The huge noise startled Parisians after a war jet was dispatched to intercept a commercial plane.
title: Parisians alarmed by sonic boom by warplane
title_page: Parisians alarmed by sonic boom by warplane - BBC News
maintext: "A very loud noise was heard in Paris and in the Paris region. It was not an explosion, it was a fighter jet breaking the sound barrier," French police wrote on Twitter on Wednesday lunchtime, urging people not to call.
